Now I don't remember well, if you could post more about your own experiences ... that would be great. Maybe I was really lucky, or I dunno ... try and report back <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
I don't loot the barracudas by the way (fresh fishes + fish scales), so there is no loot at all, and it tends to do a fish graveyard pretty fast with like 10 corpses heh. Just hit F8 with the spawning spot in front of you till you see a target and send the pet.<br>
<br>
