<br>
              l-------entrance to building... maurader spawn<br>
              V<br>
         _ _ _ _ _<br>
         l2        2l<br>
 here &gt;l           l  &lt;---here<br>
         l           l<br>
         l2_ _ _ 2l<br>
<br>
the '2' represents spawns of 2....Its a very bad map )<br>
<br>
the fish I was killing didn't seem to hit over 83, but I only killed 3 of them, didn't seem worth the mana at 44... <br>
<br>
But yes, it is a confirmed 40 second spawn, just enough time to med to full<br>
